  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>Szuriel's weapon is Lamentation of the Faithless, a black-bladed +5 speed unholy greatsword. When using the blade to attack, Szuriel regains 1d6 hit points with each successful hit. If Szuriel presents her sword  as a standard action, all creatures within 60 feet that view it are blinded and affected by crushing despair for 1d4+1 rounds unless they succeed at a DC 30 Will save. Creatures with the good subtype and divine spellcasters take a -4 penalty on this save. As a standard action, Szuriel can call the sword to her hand from any distance, including across planar boundaries.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +5 speed unholy greatsword</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p></p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>PFRPG Bestiary 6",
